Contributing Authors to INLPO Publications

inl-authors.Rmd

The 253 authors who have contributed to the 366 publications scientific monitoring and research conducted by the U.S. Geological Survey (USGS), Idaho Water Science Center, Idaho National Laboratory Project Office (INLPO) during 1949 through 2022 are provided in table 1.

Table 1.   Reference information about authors, the number of publications, and the range of years published.

[Author name: is the surname first and initials or given name. Hyperlinks to the ORCiD identifier and (or) email address are located to the right of the authors name if they are available. Total publications: is the total number of publications. Single-authored: is the number of single-authored publications. Multi-authored: is the number of multi-authored publications. First-authored: is the number of multi-authored publications where the researcher appears as first author. First year: is the first-year published. Last year: is the last-year published.]
